## 2026-04-03 - Server renameSet and snapshot restore non-atomic multi-step mutation windows
- **renameSet fix**: In `token-store.ts`, the rollback branch now only deletes the `$rename-pending.json` marker after a confirmed successful rollback. If rollback itself fails, the marker is left so `recoverPendingRename()` can complete the themes update on next startup. Changed lines ~684-695.
- **Restore journal**: Added `RestoreJournal` interface and `journalPath` field to `ManualSnapshotStore`. Added `writeRestoreJournal()` (tmp-then-rename, atomic) and `deleteRestoreJournal()` helpers.
- **Journaled restore()**: Rewrote `restore()` to write a journal before touching any token files, advance `completedSets` checkpoint after each successful set write, and delete the journal only on full success. On crash, the journal survives so recovery can replay remaining sets.

